TITLE: Caching Container Resolutions
DESCRIPTION: Example showing the container's internal caching mechanism using a singleton counter. Demonstrates cache invalidation and resolution.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jeffijoe/awilix/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
let counter = 1
container.register({
  count: asFunction(() => counter++).singleton(),
})

container.cradle.count === 1
container.cradle.count === 1

container.cache.delete('count')
container.cradle.count === 2
```

