TITLE: Setting RESOLVER Property for Non-Default Exports in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to set the RESOLVER property on a non-default export to enable auto-loading in Awilix.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jeffijoe/awilix/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const { RESOLVER } = require('awilix')
export class ServiceClass {}
ServiceClass[RESOLVER] = {}
```

