TITLE: Setting RESOLVER Property for Non-Default Exports in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows a more concise way to set the RESOLVER property on a class for auto-loading in TypeScript.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jeffijoe/awilix/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { RESOLVER } from 'awilix'
export class ServiceClass {
