TITLE: Container Options Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to access container configuration options that were passed during creation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jeffijoe/awilix/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const container = createContainer({
  injectionMode: InjectionMode.CLASSIC,
})

console.log(container.options.injectionMode) // 'CLASSIC'
